data.title: Marisa Ryan
data.meta_description: Marisa Ryan. Actress: Wet Hot American Summer. Marisa Ryan was born on 20 November 1974 in New York City, New York, USA. She is an actress and director, known for Wet Hot American Summer (2001), Unterwegs mit Jungs (2001) and Cold Hearts (1999). She has been married to Nathan Graf since 19 June 2008. She was previously married to Jeremy Sisto.
